{
  "stem": "25651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you see, that was the first that I saw that my mother was beginning to regard us both as independent of her, that she had other things to worry about, and I wasn't the priority, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That sort of growing up, you know, that sort of realization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other realization, we, we march evening, towards evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It gets dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had this huge rucksack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's about a mile and a half from Bohusovice to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I sort of stumbled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Melosh ?] said, it's not much longer, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Keep it up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from the tone of his voice, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I could see he loved me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the scraps that we had, you know, when we were much smaller children, and when I knew he was jealous of me, were forgotten, like in a-- like it's, it's different, suddenly.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, we get into the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Leo takes us out of the quarantine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh, you go through something called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] in Theresienstadt was where you were supposed to be deloused.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we came clean, you know, from, from home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you're supposed to be deloused.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you have to get completely undressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything is examined.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all the valuables that we were told to bring with us are taken off you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it's, it's robbery, you see, the, the-- you see that the internment is, in fact, robbery, because any money, everything is-- but everything that's confiscated is written down, you know, as if you're going to get it after the war.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we did have money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did have some [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] diamonds and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, clothes, spare clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, linen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Blanket, the blanket around.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
